{"tid":946493,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"訪日旅客首破3000萬 創新高","createTime":"2018-12-18T14:24:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-18T14:27:31.000Z","uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9fb5510286f8f7064e8e0447f0ae4adc6b237c3a","tid":946493,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T14:24:17.000Z","msg":"日本觀光廳表示，今年訪日旅客逾3000萬人次，創歷來新高；亞洲特別是來自中國、南韓、台灣和香港的遊客再次增加。<br />\n<br />\n官員表示，颱風飛燕曾經令大阪關西機場關閉，以及北海道地震，令訪日遊客一度減少，但其後人數逐漸回升。<br />\n<br />\n內閣官房長官菅義偉稱，希望2020年訪日旅客增至4000萬人次。<br />\n<br />\n國土交通大臣石井啟一亦稱，希望日本可以擴闊客源，不同國家地區的遊客都到訪當地。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2018657/%E8%A8%AA%E6%97%A5%E6%97%85%E5%AE%A2%E9%A6%96%E7%A0%B43000%E8%90%AC+%E5%89%B5%E6%96%B0%E9%AB%98\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2018657%2F%25E8%25A8%25AA%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%2597%2585%25E5%25AE%25A2%25E9%25A6%2596%25E7%25A0%25B43000%25E8%2590%25AC%2B%25E5%2589%25B5%25E6%2596%25B0%25E9%25AB%2598&d=qAjeUnq431rM%2BBBwyK7HkWi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=c561a517\" target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2018657/%E8%A8%AA%E6%97%A5%E6%97%85%E5%AE%A2%E9%A6%96%E7%A0%B43000%E8%90%AC+%E5%89%B5%E6%96%B0%E9%AB%98</a>"},{"pid":"c69c3b4cf82cb5f19c82a84923cc827fba80e982","tid":946493,"uid":23635,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T14:27:31.000Z","msg":"強国，南韓呢兩個國家咁憎日本，點解咁多人去日本旅遊？唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}